The paper involves training neural networks to learn programs, mathematics, or logic from data, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also utilizes symbolic expressions and tree LSTMs, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves function evaluation, which is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV).
